            <h3 class="articles__section_title">
                How to: set location name
            </h3>
            <p>
                Look at the "Select Active Layer" menu section. The active layer should be highlighted in red. Switch to the overlay layer and right-click a tile on the map.
            </p>
            <img
                src="/img/select-layer.png"
                alt="Layer selection menu"
                class="articles__section_image"
            />
            <p>
                Enter the location name and click "Save".
            </p>
            <img
                src="/img/set-location.png"
                alt="Location name input"
                class="articles__section_image"
            />
        </div>
